#: ../../../CHANGES.rst:32
msgid ""
"``CommandStart(deep_link=False)`` now correctly rejects messages that "
"contain deep-link arguments. Previously ``deep_link=False`` (the default)"
" did not distinguish between ``/start`` and ``/start <payload>``. The "
"default is changed to ``None`` (accept both) to preserve backward "
"compatibility. `#1713 <https://github.com/aiogram/aiogram/issues/1713>`_"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../CHANGES.rst:34
msgid ""
"Fixed ``HtmlDecoration.custom_emoji()`` to use the correct ``emoji-id`` "
"attribute name instead of ``emoji_id`` in the ``<tg-emoji>`` tag, "
"matching the Telegram Bot API specification. `#1782 "
"<https://github.com/aiogram/aiogram/issues/1782>`_"
msgstr ""

